# SentinelReviewAI Environment Configuration

## Development Environment

```bash
# Backend
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=4000

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://sentinel:sentinel_dev_password@localhost:5432/sentinel_review_ai

# Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=dev_jwt_secret_change_in_production
JWT_EXPIRY=7d
API_KEY=dev_api_key

# Git Provider Webhooks
GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=dev_github_secret
GITLAB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=dev_gitlab_secret
BITBUCKET_WEBHOOK_SECRET=dev_bitbucket_secret

# Git Provider API Tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token
GITLAB_TOKEN=glpat-your_gitlab_token
BITBUCKET_USERNAME=your_username
BITBUCKET_APP_PASSWORD=your_app_password

# AI Configuration
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your_openai_api_key
AI_MODEL=gpt-4
AI_MAX_TOKENS=4000
AI_TEMPERATURE=0.3

# File Analysis
MAX_FILE_SIZE=1048576
MAX_FILES_PER_REVIEW=100

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=debug
LOG_FORMAT=json
```

## Production Environment

```bash
# Backend
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=4000

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@prod-db-host:5432/sentinel_review_ai

# Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://prod-redis-host:6379

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your_secure_jwt_secret_min_32_chars
JWT_EXPIRY=1d
API_KEY=your_secure_api_key

# Git Provider Webhooks
GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_github_webhook_secret
GITLAB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_gitlab_webhook_secret
BITBUCKET_WEBHOOK_SECRET=your_bitbucket_webhook_secret

# Git Provider API Tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token
GITLAB_TOKEN=glpat-your_gitlab_token
BITBUCKET_USERNAME=your_username
BITBUCKET_APP_PASSWORD=your_app_password

# AI Configuration
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your_openai_api_key
AI_MODEL=gpt-4
AI_MAX_TOKENS=4000
AI_TEMPERATURE=0.3

# File Analysis
MAX_FILE_SIZE=1048576
MAX_FILES_PER_REVIEW=100

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=1000

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=info
LOG_FORMAT=json
```

## Environment Variables Reference

| Variable | Required | Description | Default |
|----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| `NODE_ENV` | Yes | Environment (development/staging/production) | development |
| `PORT` | Yes | Service port | 4000 |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Yes | PostgreSQL connection string | - |
| `REDIS_URL` | Yes | Redis connection string | - |
| `JWT_SECRET` | Yes | Secret for JWT signing | - |
| `JWT_EXPIRY` | No | JWT token expiry | 7d |
| `API_KEY` | Yes | API key for service authentication | - |
| `GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | No | GitHub webhook secret | - |
| `GITLAB_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | No | GitLab webhook secret | - |
| `BITBUCKET_WEBHOOK_SECRET` | No | Bitbucket webhook secret | - |
| `GITHUB_TOKEN` | No | GitHub API token | - |
| `GITLAB_TOKEN` | No | GitLab API token | - |
| `BITBUCKET_USERNAME` | No | Bitbucket username | - |
| `BITBUCKET_APP_PASSWORD` | No | Bitbucket app password | - |
| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | No | OpenAI API key | - |
| `AI_MODEL` | No | AI model to use | gpt-4 |
| `AI_MAX_TOKENS` | No | Max tokens for AI response | 4000 |
| `AI_TEMPERATURE` | No | AI temperature setting | 0.3 |
| `MAX_FILE_SIZE` | No | Max file size in bytes | 1048576 |
| `MAX_FILES_PER_REVIEW` | No | Max files per review | 100 |
| `RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS` | No | Rate limit window in ms | 60000 |
| `RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS` | No | Max requests per window | 100 |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | No | Logging level | info |
| `LOG_FORMAT` | No | Log format (json/text) | json |

## Service-Specific Ports

| Service | Port | Description |
|---------|------|-------------|
| API Gateway | 4000 | Main entry point |
| Git Integration | 4001 | Git provider integration |
| AI Review Engine | 4002 | AI code analysis |
| Context Engine | 4003 | Codebase context |
| Policy Engine | 4004 | Policy enforcement |
| Webhook Listener | 4005 | Webhook receiver |
| Analytics | 4006 | Analytics service |
| Learning Engine | 4007 | ML learning |
| Merge Gate | 4008 | Merge validation |
| Frontend | 3000 | Web dashboard |
